tutorialPages.messageText: NSLOCTEXT("[E4D20BA648F08F07691FD6BAA26EEB4A]", "BE8305584A0668A770D5EFB7D7DD6B5A", "When you run out of room to collect new items, check your invenory by pressing \'i\' or clicking on the bag icon in the menu bar.")

NSLOCTEXT("[E4D20BA648F08F07691FD6BAA26EEB4A]", "3E565B894A356EFC936C90887BB618B4", "Every resource has its own shape and size, so you may need to move things around in your Resource Bag to make space.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E4D20BA648F08F07691FD6BAA26EEB4A]", "7D3C351F4969E7AE9861779835312819", "You can also acquire and equip additional bags to carry oddly-shaped items or simply for added capacity.")
